    <h1>How to Make Chocolate Cookies</h1>
    <style>
      p.exl {
        font-style: "Times New Roman", serif;}
    </style>
    <p>
      Chocolate Chip Cookies are  <strong>amazing</strong> treats that are uasally enjoyed with a cold glass of milk. They were invented by an American chef Ruth Graves Wakefield. 
    </p>
